text: This obsoletes IRM 11.3.19, Disclosure of Official Information, Privacy Act Accounting for Disclosures.

The material relating to Disclosure of Official Information, Privacy Act Accounting for Disclosures, previously contained in IRM 11.3.19, is incorporated into the new IRM 10.5.6.7, Privacy and Information Protection, Privacy Act, Privacy Act Accounting for Disclosures, revision dated
